PrecisConfirmation of a SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT between the Crown, the Province of Ontario and THE WIKWEMIKONG INDIAN BAND which provides for the setting apart of some 24,000 acres of land for that band and the making of a compensatory payment in respect of a claim pertaining to an acreage shortfall in the 1851 survey of Point Grondine Indian Reserve No. 3.
